</a>

    </div>
  
  <div class="card-inset-details__body">

          <div class="card-inset-details__title">
        <a href="/us/blog/decade-of-childhood/202309/more-than-shy" title="More Than Shy"> More Than Shy </a>
      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            Many of our children experience shyness. This is entirely normal. For a select group of children and adolescents, however, this experience can become debilitating.
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>


  
    

